title: Vienna Symphonic Library Pro + VSL Cube Pro Strings [GigaStudio]
description:
=======[ Info ]======================================================================

Product: Vienna Symphonic Library Pro + VSL Symphonic Cube Pro Strings
Vendor: Vienna Symphonic Library GmbH
Format: [ISO]GigaStudio 3
Website: vsl.co.at


More than 300,000 violin samples and an estimated one million samples for the full library make Vienna Dimension Strings the most ambitious and intensive production in the history of the Vienna Symphonic Library.

The 24 string players of Vienna Dimension Strings were recorded in homogenous groups of 8 violins, 6 violas, 6 cellos and 4 double basses. Individual microphones for each player provide unlimited individual performance flexibility.
